WEBVTT

00:00:14.171 --> 00:00:16.490
Stari su Grci imali sjajnu ideju:

00:00:16.490 --> 00:00:18.328
svemir je jednostavan.

00:00:18.328 --> 00:00:19.288
Mislili su

00:00:19.288 --> 00:00:21.450
da se sastoji od samo 4 elementa:

00:00:21.450 --> 00:00:22.041
zemlje,

00:00:22.041 --> 00:00:22.569
zraka,

00:00:22.569 --> 00:00:23.125
vatre

00:00:23.125 --> 00:00:24.565
i vode.

00:00:24.565 --> 00:00:26.921
Lijepa je to teorija.

00:00:26.921 --> 00:00:28.898
Jednostavna i elegantna.

00:00:28.898 --> 00:00:30.314
Prema njoj, različitim